```{r setup, include = FALSE}
begin_time <-Sys.time()
suppressWarnings(source("./R/sources.R"))
library(vtable)
sumup <- function(i){
  print(i)
  print(z0n(i))
  # all data
  print(summary(z0u(i)))
  print("------------------------------------")
}
sumup2 <- function(i){
  print(i)
  print(z0n(i))
  # numeric data
  data_num <- select_if(z0u(i), is.numeric) 
  print(summary(data_num))
  print("------------------------------------")
}
```
